Core module test contract\n```\n\n### 2. .github Directory / CI/CD Configuration\n\n**Current state: NO `.github/` directory exists.** The project has zero GitHub Actions workflows at present.\n\nHowever, **AR-034** (`changes/AR-034/`) is a fully specified proposal to create 12 GitHub Actions workflows:\n\n| # | Workflow File | Purpose |\n|---|--------------|---------|\n| 1 | `main.yml` | Docker build on PR to main/release-* |\n| 2 | `lint.yml` | Go lint (golangci-lint) with path filtering |\n| 3 | `test-coverage.yml` | Race-enabled coverage tests with optional Codecov upload |\n| 4 | `e2e.yml` | E2E testing on Kind cluster (v0.30.0) |\n| 5 | `codegen-check.yml` | Code generation drift detection |\n| 6 | `copyright-check.yml` | Copyright header verification |\n| 7 | `codespell.yml` | Spelling check |\n| 8 | `python-sdk-tests.yml` | Python SDK pytest on sdk-python changes |\n| 9 | `python-lint.yml` | Python lint with Ruff |\n| 10 | `build-push-release.yml` | Multi-arch image push to GHCR |\n| 11 | `dify-plugin-publish.yml` | Dify plugin packaging and PR submission |\n| 12 | `workflows-approve.yml` | Auto-approve workflows for repeat contributors |\n\nThe `ci-cd/design.md` and `ci-cd/spec.md` files contain detailed specifications for all 12 workflows, including path filter configurations, Go/Python version matrices, Kind setup, and E2E test infrastructure.\n\n### 3. Design Docs, Specs, and Architecture Documents\n\nThe project follows a **Spec-Driven Development (SDD)** methodology with extensive documentation:\n\n**Root-level docs:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/project.md` -- Project overview, tech stack, architecture diagram\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md` -- AR-029: SDK HTTP client design (792 lines, extremely detailed)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md` -- AR-028: AgentRuntimeClient proposal\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md` -- AR-029 delta spec (366 lines)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/tasks.md` -- AR-023: CLI tasks\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/test_spec.md` -- Test specification\n\n**Per-subsystem docs (each has design.md + spec.md):**\n- `ci-cd/` -- CI/CD pipeline design and spec\n- `cli-toolkit/` -- CLI toolkit\n- `code-execution/` -- Code execution engine\n- `deployment/` -- Deployment + client-go docs\n- `idle-cleanup/` -- Idle cleanup controller\n- `integrations/` -- Integrations\n- `python-sdk/` -- Python SDK\n- `sandbox-orchestration/` -- Sandbox orchestration\n- `session-routing/` -- Session routing\n- `session-store/` -- Session store\n\n**Testing:**\n- `testing/agentcube_tdd_manifest.md` -- TDD manifest defining required test cases per module (Test-WM-1 through Test-CLI-1)\n\n**AR-034 docs:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-034/proposal.md` -- Full proposal (148 lines)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-034/design.md` -- Design template (mostly TODOs, 57 lines)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-034/tasks.md` -- Tasks template (mostly TODOs, 32 lines)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-034/delta-spec.md` -- Detailed delta spec (606 lines, all 12 workflows specified)\n\n### 4. Project Purpose, Tech Stack, and Language\n\n**Purpose:** AgentCube is a **Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents**. It provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through session-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\n\n**Architecture:**\n```\nClient / SDK / CLI\n  -> Router (Deployment :8080)\n     <-> Redis/Valkey (session store)\n     -> WorkloadManager (Service :8080)\n        <-> Redis/Valkey\n        -> K8s API: CRDs, Sandbox, Pod, Secret, TokenReview\n  Sandbox Pods (with optional PicoD daemon)\n  Agentd (idle cleanup controller)\n  Optional: Volcano vc-agent-scheduler\n```\n\n**Tech Stack:**\n\n| Layer | Technology |\n|-------|-----------|\n| **Language (server)** | Go 1.24/1.25, module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\n| **Language (CLI/SDK)** | Python >= 3.9/3.10 |\n| **HTTP framework** | Gin (Go), Typer (Python CLI) |\n| **Kubernetes** | CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, agent-sandbox |\n| **Storage** | Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go) |\n| **Auth** | JWT RS256 (golang-jwt/v5), K8s TokenReview |\n| **Packaging** | Helm 3, multi-stage Docker |\n| **Docs** | Docusaurus 3.x |\n| **CI/CD** | GitHub Actions (planned, not yet implemented) |\n\n**Go binaries (4):**\n- `router` -- Session-aware HTTP proxy/router\n- `workloadmanager` -- Control plane (session lifecycle, K8s resource management)\n- `agentd` -- Idle cleanup controller\n- `picod` -- Code execution sandbox daemon\n\n**Python packages (2):**\n- `agentcube-sdk` (`python-sdk/`) -- Python SDK with `CodeInterpreterClient` and `AgentRuntimeClient`\n- `agentcube` CLI (`cmd/cli/`) -- Python CLI tool\n\n### 5. AR-034 and ST-1 Related Files\n\n**AR-034 files (CI/CD GitHub Actions):**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-034/proposal.md` -- Complete proposal for 12 workflows\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-034/design.md` -- Design template (TODO placeholders)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-034/tasks.md` -- Tasks template (TODO placeholders)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-034/delta-spec.md` -- Full delta spec with all 12 workflows detailed (606 lines)\n\n**ST-1 references found:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/.sdd_prompt.md` (line 463): `[Stage ST-1 completed]` -- indicates the proposal stage was completed\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/tasks.md` (line 3): `Stage: ST-1 (Proposal)` -- AR-003 is at the proposal stage\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/testing/agentcube_tdd_manifest.md` (line 23): `Test-ST-1` -- a test case for Session Store serialization/deserialization\n\n### 6. Build/Config Files\n\n**Go:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/go.mod` -- Module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`, Go 1.25.0, ~20 direct dependencies (gin, go-redis, valkey, controller-runtime, k8s.io/*, jwt, etc.)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/go.sum` -- Dependency checksums\n\n**Python SDK:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/pyproject.toml` -- Package `agentcube-sdk` v0.1.0, requires Python >= 3.9, deps: requests, PyJWT>=2.0.0, cryptography, setuptools build\n\n**Python CLI:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/pyproject.toml` -- CLI package (exists, not read in detail)\n\n**Makefile:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/Makefile` -- 186 lines, AR-033, targets: `all`, `build`, `clean`, `test`, `test-coverage`, `test-chart`, `lint`, `fmt`, `vet`, `docker`, `helm-lint`, `helm-template`, `python-lint`, `python-test`, `ci