d in `ci-cd/design.md`):**\n- Kind cluster v0.30.0 (`agentcube-e2e`)\n- agent-sandbox CRDs v0.1.1\n- Helm deployment of AgentCube chart\n- Go E2E tests (`go test -v ./test/e2e/...`)\n- Python E2E tests (`test_codeinterpreter.py`)\n- Port-forwarding for Workload Manager (8080) and Router (8081)\n- Log artifact collection on failure\n\n**Changes directory (34 ARs):**\n- AR-001 through AR-034, each with proposal.md, design.md, tasks.md, and optionally delta-spec.md\n- AR-034 is the CI/CD proposal (the most recent)\n- AR-033 is the Makefile unification\n- AR-032 is Dockerfile multi-stage builds\n- AR-028/AR-029 are Python SDK related\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_28560b4d1ffe7kVq4JIuenPQdN","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775878753065,"end":1775878948883}}}}
