{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775878968962,"sessionID":"ses_28560f931ffe4C5vIqrKBCG3xA","part":{"id":"prt_d7aa2967f0017qN9yVLoeLMxKx","messageID":"msg_d7aa28da0001zijmqhhD0EaEnC","sessionID":"ses_28560f931ffe4C5vIqrKBCG3xA","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775879143967,"sessionID":"ses_28560f931ffe4C5vIqrKBCG3xA","part":{"id":"prt_d7aa2a0e7001TARGh9wv57Pv1E","messageID":"msg_d7aa28da0001zijmqhhD0EaEnC","sessionID":"ses_28560f931ffe4C5vIqrKBCG3xA","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_70ead93e0b5e460b8794aa7b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-034: CI/CD GitHub Actions (12 workflows) — Design/设计说明\n\n## 1. 架构 (Architecture)\n\n### 1.1 定位 (Purpose/Positioning)\n\n为 AgentCube 项目建立完整的 GitHub Actions CI/CD 流水线体系，覆盖以下职责：\n\n1. **PR 门禁验证** — Docker 构建、Go lint、race-enabled 覆盖率测试、Kind E2E 测试、代码生成漂移检测、版权/拼写检查、Python SDK 测试与 lint\n2. **自动发布** — 推送 `main` 或语义化版本 tag 时构建并推送多架构容器镜像到 GHCR\n3. **插件发布** — `dify-plugin/v*` tag 时打包 Dify 插件并自动提交 PR 到 `langgenius/dify-plugins`\n4. **贡献者体验** — 自动审批非首次贡献者或带 `ok-to-test` 标签的 pending workflow runs\n\n本 AR 不修改任何现有源码、Dockerfile、Helm chart 或 Makefile，仅消费 AR-033 定义的 Makefile 目标。\n\n### 1.2 系统上下文 (System Context)\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                        GitHub Repository                                │\n│                                                                         │\n│  PR to main/release-*                                                   │\n│    ├── main.yml ─────────────── make docker-build                       │\n│    ├── lint.yml ─────────────── make lint [if *.go changed]             │\n│    ├── test-coverage.yml ────── go test -race -cover [if code changed]  │\n│    ├── e2e.yml ──────────────── make e2e on Kind v0.30.0                │\n│    ├── codegen-check.yml ────── make gen-check [if API/hack changed]    │\n│    ├── copyright-check.yml ─── make gen-copyright + git diff            │\n│    ├── codespell.yml ────────── codespell scan                          │\n│    ├── python-sdk-tests.yml ─── pytest [if sdk-python/ changed]         │\n│    └── python-lint.yml ──────── ruff check [if python changed]          │\n│                                                                         │\n│  Push to main or tag v*.*.*                                             │\n│    └── build-push-release.yml ── multi-arch build + push to ghcr.io     │\n│                                                                         │\n│  Tag dify-plugin/v*                                                     │\n│    └── dify-plugin-publish.yml ── package + PR to langgenius/dify-plugins│\n│                                                                         │\n│  PR labeled/synchronize                                                 │\n│    └── workflows-approve.yml ──── auto-approve pending runs             │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                              │\n                              ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                     Makefile Targets (AR-033)                           │\n│  docker-build | lint | gen-check | gen-copyright | e2e | e2e-clean      │\n│  docker-buildx-push-workloadmanager | docker-buildx-push-router          │\n│  docker-buildx-push-picod                                                │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n### 1.3 目录结构 (Directory Layout)\n\n**当前状态 (Before):**\n\n```\n(no .github/ directory)\n```\n\n**目标状态 (After):**\n\n```\n.github/\n└── workflows/\n    ├── main.yml                      # Agentcube CI Workflow\n    ├── lint.yml                      # Go Lint\n    ├── test-coverage.yml             # Test Coverage\n    ├── e2e.yml                       # E2E Tests\n    ├── codegen-check.yml             # Codegen Check\n    ├── copyright-check.yml           # Copyright Check\n    ├── codespell.yml                 # Codespell\n    ├── python-sdk-tests.yml          # Python SDK Tests\n    ├── python-lint.yml               # Python Lint\n    ├── build-push-release.yml        # Build and Push Release Images\n    ├── dify-plugin-publish.yml       # Dify Plugin Publish\n    └── workflows-approve.yml         # Approve Workflows\n```\n\n### 1.4 依赖关系 (Dependencies)\n\n| 依赖 | 来源 | 用途 |\n|------|------|------|\n| AR-033 (Makefile) | 现有 Makefile | 所有 workflow 消费的构建/测试/发布目标 |\n| AR-032 (Dockerfile) | docker/Dockerfile, Dockerfile.router, Dockerfile.picod | main.yml 和 build-push-release.yml 的镜像构建 |\n| actions/checkout@v4 | GitHub Actions | 所有 workflow 的代码检出 |\n| actions/setup-go@v5 | GitHub Actions | Go 环境安装 (1.23/1.24/1.24.4) |\n| actions/setup-python@v5 | GitHub Actions | Python 环境安装 (3.10/3.12) |\n| docker/setup-buildx-action@v3 | GitHub Actions | Docker Buildx 设置 |\n| docker/login-action@v3 | GitHub Actions | GHCR 登录 |\n| docker/build-push-action@v6 | GitHub Actions | 多架构镜像构建推送 |\n| dorny/paths-filter@v3 | 社区 Action | 路径过滤按需触发 |\n| helm/kind-action@v1 | 社区 Action | Kind 集群安装 (install_only: true) |\n| codecov/codecov-action@v5 | 社区 Action | 覆盖率报告上传 (可选) |\n| peter-evans/create-pull-request@v7 | 社区 Action | Dify 插件 PR 提交 |\n| actions/github-script@v7 | GitHub Actions | workflows-approve.yml 中的 API 调用 |\n\n**上游 AR 依赖图:**\n\n```\nAR-033 (Makefile) ──┬── AR-034 (CI/CD workflows)\nAR-032 (Dockerfile)─┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## 2. 数据结构 (Data Structures)\n\n### 2.1 Workflow 触发配置矩阵\n\n| Workflow | Events | Branches/Tags | Path Filter |\n|----------|--------|---------------|-------------|\n| main.yml | `pull_request` | `main`, `release-*` | None (always runs) |\n| lint.yml | `pull_request` | `main`, `release-*` | `lint`: `**/*.go`, `go.mod`, `go.sum`, `.golangci.yml`, `.github/workflows/lint.yml` |\n| test-coverage.yml | `pull_request`, `merge_group`, `workflow_call` | `main` (PR only) | `coverage`: `**` minus `*.md`, `*.svg`, `*.png` |\n| e2e.yml | `pull_request` | `main`, `release-*` | None (always runs) |\n| codegen-check.yml | `pull_request` | `main`, `release-*` | `codegen`: `pkg/apis/**`, `hack/**`, `.github/workflows/**`, `Makefile` |\n| copyright-check.yml | `pull_request` | `main`, `release-*` | `copyright`: all minus `*.md`, `*.svg`, `*.png`, `docs/**`, `.github/**` |\n| codespell.yml | `pull_request` | `main`, `release-*` | None (always runs) |\n| python-sdk-tests.yml | `pull_request`, `merge_group` | — | `sdk`: `sdk-python/**` |\n| python-lint.yml | `pull_request` | `main`, `release-*` | `python`: `cmd/cli/**`, `sdk-python/**`, `example/**`, `test/**/*.py`, `pyproject.toml` |\n| build-push-release.yml | `push` | `main`, tags `v*.*.*`, `v*.*.*-*` | None |\n| dify-plugin-publish.yml | `push` | tags `dify-plugin/v*` | None |\n| workflows-approve.yml | `pull_request_target` types `labeled`, `synchronize` | `main`, `release-**` | None (logic-based) |\n\n### 2.2 运行时环境配置\n\n#### Go 版本分配\n\n| Workflow | Go Version | Rationale |\n|----------|------------|-----------|\n| lint.yml | `1.24` | 与项目 go.mod (1.25.0) 兼容的最小稳定版 |\n| test-coverage.yml | `1.24` | 覆盖 `pkg/...` 单元测试 |\n| e2e.yml | `1.23` | Kind 集群兼容性要求 |\n| codegen-check.yml | `1.24.4` | 代码生成工具的精确版本锁定 |\n| build-push-release.yml | `1.24.4` | 发布构建的精确版本锁定 |\n\n#### Python 版本分配\n\n| Workflow | Python Version | Rationale |\n|----------|----------------|-----------|\n| python-sdk-tests.yml | `3.12` | SDK 测试的最新稳定版 |\n| python-lint.yml | `3.10` | 与 SDK `requires-python >= 3.9` 兼容的 lint 基线 |\n| codespell.yml | system default | 仅运行 `pip install codespell`，不依赖特定版本 |\n\n#### Runner 选择\n\n| Workflow | Runner | Rationale |\n|----------|--------|-----------|\n| main.yml | `ubuntu-latest` | Docker 构建需要 Linux |\n| lint.yml | `ubuntu-latest` | golangci-lint 跨平台 |\n| test-coverage.yml | `ubuntu-latest` | Go 测试 |\n| e2e.yml | `ubuntu-24.04` (or larger) | Kind 集群需要充足资源 |\n| codegen-check.yml | `ubuntu-latest` | 代码生成检查 |\n| copyright-check.yml | `ubuntu-latest` | 版权检查 |\n| codespell.yml | `ubuntu-latest` | 拼写检查 |\n| python-sdk-tests.yml | `ubuntu-latest` | Python 测试 |\n| python-lint.yml | `ubuntu-latest` | Python lint |\n| build-push-release.yml | `ubuntu-latest` | Docker 多架构构建 |\n| dify-plugin-publish.yml | `ubuntu-latest` | 插件打包和 PR 提交 |\n| workflows-approve.yml | `ubuntu-latest` | GitHub API 调用 |\n\n### 2.3 Secret 配置\n\n| Secret | Scope | Required | Usage |\n|--------|-------|----------|-------|\n| `GITHUB_TOKEN` | 自动提供 | Yes | GHCR 登录 (build-push-release.yml)、cross-repo PR (dify-plugin-publish.yml)、workflow 审批 (workflows-approve.yml) |\n| `CODECOV_TOKEN` | 仓库设置 | No | 覆盖率报告上传 (test-coverage.yml)，缺失时跳过 |\n| `PLUGIN_ACTION` | 仓库设置 | Yes | Dify 插件发布时访问 `langgenius/dify-plugins` 仓库的 PAT |\n\n### 2.4 环境变量\n\n#### build-push-release.yml\n\n| Variable | Value | Purpose |\n|----------|-------|---------|\n| `TAG` | `latest` (push to main) or `github.ref_name` (tag push) | 镜像 tag |\n| `IMAGE_REGISTRY` | `ghcr.io/${{ github.repository_owner }}` | 镜像仓库地址 |\n| `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_IMAGE` | `workloadmanager:${TAG}` | Workload Manager 镜像名 |\n| `ROUTER_IMAGE` | `router:${TAG}` | Router 镜像名 |\n| `PICOD_IMAGE` | `picod:${TAG}` | PicoD 镜像名 |\n\n#### e2e.yml\n\n| Variable | Value | Purpose |\n|----------|-------|---------|\n| `ARTIFACTS_PATH` | `${{ github.workspace }}/e2e-logs` | E2E 日志收集路径 |\n\n### 2.5 路径过滤配置详情\n\n#### lint filter\n\n```yaml\nlint:\n  - '**/*.go'\n  - 'go.mod'\n  - 'go.sum'\n  - '.golangci.yml'\n  - '.github/workflows/lint.yml'\n```\n\n#### coverage filter\n\n```yaml\ncoverage:\n  - '**'\n  - '!*.md'\n  - '!*.svg'\n  - '!*.png'\n```\n\n#### codegen filter\n\n```yaml\ncodegen:\n  - 'pkg/apis/**'\n  - 'hack/**'\n  - '.github/workflows/**'\n  - 'Makefile'\n```\n\n#### copyright filter\n\n```yaml\ncopyright:\n  - '**'\n  - '!*.md'\n  - '!*.svg'\n  - '!*.png'\n  - '!docs/**'\n  - '!.github/**'\n```\n\n#### sdk filter\n\n```yaml\nsdk:\n  - 'sdk-python/**'\n```\n\n#### python filter\n\n```yaml\npython:\n  - 'cmd/cli/**'\n  - 'sdk-python/**'\n  - 'example/**'\n  - 'test/**/*.py'\n  - 'pyproject.toml'\n```\n\n---\n\n## 3. API 契约 (API Contracts)\n\n### 3.1 Makefile 目标消费契约\n\n所有 workflow 通过 `make` 命令消费 AR-033 定义的目标，不直接调用底层工具。\n\n| Workflow | Makefile Target | Expected Behavior |\n|----------|-----------------|-------------------|\n| main.yml | `make docker-build` | 构建 workloadmanager 镜像，退出码 0 表示成功 |\n| lint.yml | `make lint` | 运行 golangci-lint，退出码 0 表示无 lint 违规 |\n| test-coverage.yml | `go test -race -v -coverprofile=coverage.out -coverpkg=./pkg/... ./pkg/...` | 直接调用 go test（不通过 Makefile），生成 coverage.out |\n| e2e.yml | `make e2e` | 运行 `./test/e2e/run_e2e.sh`，包含 Kind 集群创建、CRD 安装、Helm 部署、Go/Python E2E 测试 |\n| e2e.yml (cleanup) | `make e2e-clean` | 删除 Kind 集群，清理 `/tmp/agent-sandbox` |\n| codegen-check.yml | `make gen-check` | 运行 `make gen-all` + `git diff --exit-code`，退出码 0 表示生成文件同步 |\n| copyright-check.yml | `make gen-copyright` + `git diff --exit-code` | 生成版权头，退出码 0 表示无差异 |\n| build-push-release.yml | `make docker-buildx-push-workloadmanager`, `docker-buildx-push-router`, `docker-buildx-push-picod` | 构建并推送多架构镜像到 GHCR |\n\n### 3.2 test-coverage.yml `workflow_call` 接口\n\n```yaml\non:\n  workflow_call:\n    secrets:\n      CODECOV_TOKEN:\n        required: false\n```\n\n允许其他 workflow 通过 `workflow_call` 复用覆盖率测试逻辑，`CODECOV_TOKEN` 为可选传入。\n\n### 3.3 E2E 测试环境契约\n\nE2E workflow 依赖以下基础设施（由 `make e2e` / `run_e2e.sh` 管理）：\n\n| 组件 | 版本/配置 | 用途 |\n|------|-----------|------|\n| Kind | v0.30.0 (`install_only: true`) | 轻量 K8s 集群 |\n| agent-sandbox CRDs | v0.1.1 | `manifest.yaml` + `extensions.yaml` |\n| Helm chart | `manifests/charts/base` | AgentCube 部署 |\n| Redis | `redis:7-alpine` | Session store |\n| Workload Manager | `workloadmanager:latest` | 本地构建镜像 |\n| Router | `agentcube-router:latest` | 本地构建镜像 |\n| PicoD | `picod:latest` | 本地构建镜像 |\n\n**端口转发:**\n- Workload Manager: `localhost:8080` → `svc/workloadmanager:8080`\n- Router: `localhost:8081` → `svc/agentcube-router:8080`\n\n**健康检查:**\n- `http://localhost:8080/health` (Workload Manager)\n- `http://localhost:8081/health/live` (Router)\n\n### 3.4 Dify 插件发布契约\n\n| 步骤 | 输入 | 输出 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 下载 dify-plugin CLI | version `0.0.6` | 可执行文件 |\n| 安装 yq | — | YAML 处理工具 |\n| 读取 manifest.yaml | `dify-plugin/manifest.yaml` | 插件元数据 (name, version) |\n| 打包插件 | `dify-plugin/` 目录 | `.difypkg` 文件 |\n| 创建 PR | `PLUGIN_ACTION` PAT, 插件包 | PR to `langgenius/dify-plugins` |\n\n### 3.5 Workflows Approve 契约\n\n```\nInput: pull_request_target (labeled/synchronize) on main/release-**\n\nLogic:\n  1. Query GitHub API: list PRs by author to repo\n  2. If PR count > 1 (repeat contributor) OR PR has \"ok-to-test\" label:\n     a. List workflow runs for head_sha with status=action_required\n     b. For each run: call octokit.rest.actions.approveWorkflowRun()\n  3. Else: skip (first-time contributor without label)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 4. 错误处理 (Error Handling)\n\n### 4.1 Workflow 失败策略\n\n| 场景 | 行为 | 恢复方式 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| Docker 构建失败 (main.yml) | Job 立即失败，退出码非 0 | 修复 Dockerfile 后重新触发 PR |\n| Lint 失败 (lint.yml) | Job 失败，golangci-lint 输出违规详情 | 修复代码后 push 新 commit |\n| 覆盖率测试失败 (test-coverage.yml) | Job 失败，Go test 输出失败用例 | 修复测试或代码后 push |\n| E2E 测试失败 (e2e.yml) | Job 失败，上传 `e2e-logs/` artifact | 下载日志 artifact 诊断；`make e2e-clean` 在 `always()` 中执行确保清理 |\n| 代码生成漂移 (codegen-check.yml) | `git diff --exit-code` 失败，显示差异 | 运行 `make gen-all` 重新生成后提交 |\n| 版权检查失败 (copyright-check.yml) | `git diff --exit-code` 失败 | 运行 `make gen-copyright` 后提交 |\n| Codespell 失败 (codespell.yml) | codespell 报告拼写错误 | 修正拼写或添加到 ignore list；临时文件在 `always()` 中恢复 |\n| Python 测试失败 (python-sdk-tests.yml) | pytest 退出码非 0 | 修复测试或代码后 push |\n| Python lint 失败 (python-lint.yml) | ruff 报告违规 | 运行 `ruff check --fix` 或手动修复 |\n| 发布构建失败 (build-push-release.yml) | Job 失败，镜像未推送 | 修复后重新打 tag 或 push 到 main |\n| Dify 插件发布失败 | PR 创建失败 | 检查 `PLUGIN_ACTION` secret 权限后手动重试 |\n| Workflow 审批失败 | github-script 执行错误 | 维护者手动 approve |\n\n### 4.2 资源清理保障\n\n| Workflow | Cleanup Step | Condition |\n|----------|-------------|-----------|\n| e2e.yml | `make e2e-clean` | `always()` — 无论测试成败都执行 |\n| codespell.yml | 恢复临时移动的文件 | `always()` — 无论 codespell 成败都执行 |\n\n### 4.3 可选 Secret 的优雅降级\n\n**CODECOV_TOKEN (test-coverage.yml):**\n\n```yaml\n- name: Upload coverage to Codecov\n  if: ${{ secrets.CODECOV_TOKEN != '' }}\n  uses: codecov/codecov-action@v5\n  with:\n    token: ${{ secrets.CODECOV_TOKEN }}\n```\n\n当 `CODECOV_TOKEN` 未配置时，上传步骤被跳过，workflow 不因此失败。\n\n### 4.4 路径过滤的跳过行为\n\n当 `dorny/paths-filter` 评估后 `changed` 为 `false` 时，后续 job 步骤通过 `if: steps.filter.outputs.lint == 'true'` 条件跳过。GitHub 将步骤标记为 \"Skipped\"（黄色），不影响 workflow 整体状态。\n\n### 4.5 磁盘空间保障\n\n**test-coverage.yml** 在覆盖率测试前执行 `free-disk-space` 步骤，清理 runner 上不需要的缓存和包，确保大仓库有足够空间生成覆盖率数据。\n\n---\n\n## 5. 测试策略 (Testing Strategy)\n\n### 5.1 Workflow 验证方法\n\n| 验证类型 | 方法 | 工具 |\n|----------|------|------|\n| 语法验证 | `actionlint` 静态检查 workflow YAML | `actionlint` CLI |\n| 触发验证 | 在 PR 中观察 workflow 是否按预期触发/跳过 | GitHub Actions UI |\n| 路径过滤验证 | 提交仅修改特定路径的 PR，确认对应 workflow 触发/跳过 | GitHub Actions UI |\n| 功能验证 | 观察 workflow 执行结果（成功/失败）与预期一致 | GitHub Actions UI + logs |\n| 发布验证 | 打 tag 后观察 GHCR 中是否出现对应镜像 | GHCR UI / `docker pull` |\n\n### 5.2 关键测试场景\n\n#### 5.2.1 PR 门禁验证\n\n| 场景 | 预期行为 | 验证方式 |\n|------|----------|----------|\n| PR 到 main，修改 Go 文件 | main.yml, lint.yml, test-coverage.yml, e2e.yml, codegen-check.yml, copyright-check.yml, codespell.yml 全部触发 | GitHub Actions UI |\n| PR 到 main，仅修改 `docs/README.md` | 仅 codespell.yml 触发（无路径过滤），其余跳过 | GitHub Actions UI |\n| PR 到 main，仅修改 `sdk-python/` 下文件 | python-sdk-tests.yml, python-lint.yml 触发 | GitHub Actions UI |\n| PR 到 `feature/*` | 所有 PR workflow 不触发 | GitHub Actions UI |\n| PR 到 `release-v0.1` | 与 PR 到 main 相同的 workflow 触发 | GitHub Actions UI |\n\n#### 5.2.2 发布验证\n\n| 场景 | 预期行为 | 验证方式 |\n|------|----------|----------|\n| Push 到 main | build-push-release.yml 触发，TAG=latest，3 个镜像推送到 GHCR | GHCR UI |\n| Push tag `v0.2.0` | build-push-release.yml 触发，TAG=v0.2.0，3 个镜像推送 | GHCR UI |\n| Push tag `v0.2.0-beta.1` | build-push-release.yml 触发，TAG=v0.2.0-beta.1 | GHCR UI |\n| Push tag `docs-update` | build-push-release.yml 不触发 | GitHub Actions UI |\n| Push 到 `feature/*` | build-push-release.yml 不触发 | GitHub Actions UI |\n\n#### 5.2.3 Dify 插件发布验证\n\n| 场景 | 预期行为 | 验证方式 |\n|------|----------|----------|\n| Push tag `dify-plugin/v1.0.0` | dify-plugin-publish.yml 触发，打包插件，创建 PR 到 `langgenius/dify-plugins` | 目标仓库 PR 列表 |\n| Push tag `v0.2.0` | dify-plugin-publish.yml 不触发 | GitHub Actions UI |\n\n#### 5.2.4 Workflow 审批验证\n\n| 场景 | 预期行为 | 验证方式 |\n|------|----------|----------|\n| 重复贡献者开 PR | workflows-approve.yml 自动 approve pending runs | GitHub Actions UI (无 pending 状态) |\n| 首次贡献者开 PR + `ok-to-test` 标签 | workflows-approve.yml 自动 approve | GitHub Actions UI |\n| 首次贡献者开 PR (无标签) | workflows-approve.yml 不 approve | GitHub Actions UI (pending 状态保持) |\n\n#### 5.2.5 错误场景验证\n\n| 场景 | 预期行为 | 验证方式 |\n|------|----------|----------|\n| Dockerfile 语法错误 | main.yml 失败，退出码非 0 | workflow log |\n| Go 代码有 lint 违规 | lint.yml 失败，golangci-lint 输出详情 | workflow log |\n| 生成文件未同步 | codegen-check.yml 失败，`git diff` 显示差异 | workflow log |\n| 新增文件缺少版权头 | copyright-check.yml 失败 | workflow log |\n| E2E 测试失败 | e2e.yml 失败，`e2e-logs/` artifact 上传 | workflow artifacts |\n| codespell 发现拼写错误 | codespell.yml 失败，报告错误位置 | workflow log |\n\n### 5.3 本地验证\n\n在创建 PR 前，可使用以下命令本地验证 workflow 依赖的 Makefile 目标：\n\n```bash\n# 验证 Docker 构建\nmake docker-build\n\n# 验证 Go lint\nmake lint\n\n# 验证覆盖率测试\ngo test -race -v -coverprofile=coverage.out -coverpkg=./pkg/... ./pkg/...\n\n# 验证代码生成同步\nmake gen-check\n\n# 验证版权头\nmake gen-copyright && git diff --exit-code\n\n# 验证 Python SDK 测试\ncd python-sdk && pip install -e . && python -m pytest tests/ -v\n\n# 验证 Python lint\nruff check . --config pyproject.toml\n\n# 验证 Helm chart\nmake helm-lint\n```\n\n### 5.4 回归测试策略\n\n由于本 AR 不修改任何现有代码，回归风险极低。验证重点在于：\n\n1. **Workflow 触发正确性** — 确保路径过滤配置与项目实际目录结构匹配\n2. **Makefile 目标兼容性** — 确保 workflow 调用的 Makefile 目标存在且行为符合预期\n3. **Secret 权限** — 确保 `GITHUB_TOKEN` 和 `PLUGIN_ACTION` 具有所需权限\n4. **版本兼容性** — 确保 Go/Python/Kind 版本与项目需求匹配\n\n---\n\n## 6. 实现步骤 (Implementation Steps)\n\n### Phase 1: 基础设施 Workflow (PR 门禁)\n\n1. **创建 `.github/workflows/main.yml`** — Docker 构建验证\n   - 触发: `pull_request` to `main`, `release-*`\n   - Job: checkout → setup-buildx → verify docker → `make docker-build`\n\n2. **创建 `.github/workflows/lint.yml`** — Go lint\n   - 触发: `pull_request` to `main`, `release-*`\n   - 路径过滤: `lint` filter\n   - Job: checkout → paths-filter → if changed: setup-go 1.24 → `make lint`\n\n3. **创建 `.github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`** — 覆盖率测试\n   - 触发: `pull_request`, `merge_group`, `workflow_call`\n   - 路径过滤: `coverage` filter\n   - Job: checkout → paths-filter → if changed: free-disk-space → setup-go 1.24 → `go test -race -v -coverprofile=coverage.out -coverpkg=./pkg/... ./pkg/...` → upload artifact → optional Codecov upload\n\n4. **创建 `.github/workflows/e2e.yml`** — E2E 测试\n   - 触发: `pull_request` to `main`, `release-*`\n   - Job: checkout → setup-go 1.23 → kind-action v0.30.0 (install_only) → set ARTIFACTS_PATH → `make e2e` → on failure upload logs → `always()` → `make e2e-clean`\n\n### Phase 2: 代码质量 Workflow\n\n5. **创建 `.github/workflows/codegen-check.yml`** — 代码生成检查\n   - 触发: `pull_request` to `main`, `release-*`\n   - 路径过滤: `codegen` filter\n   - Job: checkout → paths-filter → if changed: setup-go 1.24.4 → `make gen-check`\n\n6. **创建 `.github/workflows/copyright-check.yml`** — 版权检查\n   - 触发: `pull_request` to `main`, `release-*`\n   - 路径过滤: `copyright` filter\n   - Job: checkout → paths-filter → if changed: apt install moreutils → `make gen-copyright` → `git diff --exit-code`\n\n7. **创建 `.github/workflows/codespell.yml`** — 拼写检查\n   - 触发: `pull_request` to `main`, `release-*`\n   - Job: checkout → backup/remove false-positive files → pip install codespell → codespell with skips/ignores → `always()` restore files\n\n### Phase 3: Python Workflow\n\n8. **创建 `.github/workflows/python-sdk-tests.yml`** — Python SDK 测试\n   - 触发: `pull_request`, `merge_group`\n   - 路径过滤: `sdk` filter\n   - Job: checkout → paths-filter → if changed: setup-python 3.12 in sdk-python/ → pip install pytest → pip install -e . → `python -m pytest tests/ -v`\n\n9. **创建 `.github/workflows/python-lint.yml`** — Python lint\n   - 触发: `pull_request` to `main`, `release-*`\n   - 路径过滤: `python` filter\n   - Job: checkout → paths-filter → if changed: setup-python 3.10 → pip install ruff → `python3 -m ruff check . --config pyproject.toml`\n\n### Phase 4: 发布与自动化 Workflow\n\n10. **创建 `.github/workflows/build-push-release.yml`** — 多架构镜像发布\n    - 触发: `push` to `main`, tags `v*.*.*`, `v*.*.*-*`\n    - Job: checkout → setup-go 1.24.4 → setup-buildx → docker login ghcr.io → set TAG → `make docker-buildx-push-workloadmanager` → `docker-buildx-push-router` → `docker-buildx-push-picod`\n\n11. **创建 `.github/workflows/dify-plugin-publish.yml`** — Dify 插件发布\n    - 触发: `push` tags `dify-plugin/v*`\n    - Job: download dify-plugin CLI → install yq → read manifest → package plugin → checkout author/dify-plugins with PLUGIN_ACTION → move .difypkg → branch/commit/push → `gh pr create`\n\n12. **创建 `.github/workflows/workflows-approve.yml`** — 自动审批\n    - 触发: `pull_request_target` types `labeled`, `synchronize` to `main`, `release-**`\n    - Job: github-script → list contributor PRs → if not first-time or has ok-to-test → list action_required runs → approve each\n\n---\n\n## 7. 后续变更 (Follow-up Changes)\n\n| 变更 | 描述 | 优先级 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| Docusaurus 文档 CI/CD | 文档站点自动构建和部署 | 中 |\n| Reusable workflows 抽象 | 将公共的 Go/Python 设置逻辑提取为 `workflow_call` 可复用 workflow | 低 |\n| Self-hosted runners | 为 E2E 测试配置自托管 runner 以加速 Kind 集群创建 | 低 |\n| Slack/Discord 通知 | CI 失败时发送通知到团队频道 | 低 |\n| 覆盖率阈值门禁 | 设置最低覆盖率阈值，低于阈值时 PR 检查失败 | 中 |\n| Dependabot 配置 | 自动更新 GitHub Actions 依赖版本 | 中 |\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-034/design.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-034/design.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20